name: Seclusion Creeping In
description:
Surreal expression of loneliness in the
modern world and the future. Old
worlds breaking away, digital paint
begins to dominate traditional and
people are left alone to think,
secluded. Demons watch on as they
close in through the digital world to
consume what is left of humans. The
piece is mixed photography, vector
drawn and oil painted elements to suit
the piece and it's digital transitions
real/fake life. GIF 1300 x 1491
